(2, 'return_policy', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n    <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Return Policy: </span></u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:107%\">Here at\r\nSuqbahrain we believe in 100% customer service and strive to please all\r\nSuqbahrainers. We always do our best to take care of our valuable customers. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">In the unlikely event, if any product that you have sold\r\nis damaged or incorrect then the customer may return your product. To be\r\neligible for a refund, the product must be returned to </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">Suqbahrain</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\"> in a resalable &amp; unused condition, and then the\r\nproduct will be forwarded to the specified Merchant. The item shall be in the\r\noriginal packaging and returned with any accessories or free gifts within 7\r\ndays from the day it was delivered.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">The categories that cannot be returned are:</span></u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">1.<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>Used or, not in the same condition and packaging as customer receives it.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">2.&nbsp; Specific categories like innerwear, lingerie,\r\nBeauty products, perfumes/deodorant, pants, socks and clothing freebies,\r\ngrocery &amp; gourmet, Jewelry and Pet Supplies etc.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">3.&nbsp; Items which have been used or installed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">4.&nbsp; Products that have been tampered with or a\r\nmissing serial numbers.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">5.&nbsp; Products with missing labels or accessories.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">6.&nbsp; Digital products</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in\">Important Notes:<br style=\"mso-special-character:line-break\">\r\n<br style=\"mso-special-character:line-break\">\r\n</span></u></b><u></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">1.&nbsp; If you received a damaged item then you will\r\nhave to inform the shipping company within 3 days of delivery.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1\">2.&nbsp; Please make sure that all returned items are\r\npacked securely to prevent any loss or damage during transit.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '2020-08-19 05:03:55', '2020-08-18 23:03:55'),
